➜紫砂匠人魏孝朋作品欣赏——六方禅钟
http://www.sohu.com/a/351096060_528362	48960
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20191101/6ca0ac00aa964b6db133607a379d5a41.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>关键词：魏孝朋紫砂作品 清朋紫砂艺术 手工近作 线条流畅 块面过渡自然</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20191101/967346968447430d86bf8f3e5403f989.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20191101/0049b31d90c843beb120b04ca8a1dda3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20191101/41eb7b8ec8214ac5a1d4a40ae7a152a3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>六方禅钟，壶身上下皆以六方形呈现，比例协调，轮廓清晰，线条苍劲有力。其采用原矿紫泥精制而成，壶身饱满有张力，盖压盖设计契合紧密，密封性好。耳环与壶嘴自然弯曲，与壶身相应，方圆对比，正是方器的精髓所在。此壶可谓是方圆相融，方圆理念得以淋漓尽致地展现。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20191101/e6cc4decf2134c48a9b742b30c9a31b1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20191101/8d5139dc2df044a88d49ec3f91e8fecb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20191101/fa700ec38cf846b5885e7a562bd4da62.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>作品造型雅正雄劲，方圆平正，高下曲直，莫不面面俱到，于传统法度中出自家新意。线条于游走中营造出一种涓细无尘的质朴情素。此壶，是收藏的珍品，不可错过。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20191101/ea75222ee0ee49a5b5421a0659fe70fa.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20191101/019e49e989884336a3977c9347c9b160.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20191101/899a691696534cc29267a0725773e9ac.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>此款壶的冲茗特性：温和典雅，茶汤韵味悠扬、沉着持久，养泡日久，泥色由棕变幻为古黯肝色，愈显古朴素，明润光和也！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">默坐对此壶，耳畔似有深山古寺的钟鸣徐徐，声清而廉，气贞而静，自有天然逸响，其萧疏清冷之致，诚可以自相愉悦，不能赠人也。</p>